g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚頹"},{"pid":"9f1bc6373033ad6c2e7c3ea9e886b4a0a7c1f674","tid":2133071,"uid":247159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T22:42:46.000Z","msg":"有呀，唔開心情願永遠都黑夜唔想見光，所以我鐘意夜闌人靜果種感覺，可能一天光就好似要面對現實"},{"pid":"cbd17cb37ca5796246aeff15df1e724dbf937172","tid":2133071,"uid":360235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T01:14:37.000Z","msg":"無所事事係咁 對世界無咩求知欲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc64245857dd234515dbd7db227f9685110ace3","tid":2133071,"uid":343601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17ed3b2cff85721efd99e24ad840bed41456f8d5","tid":2133071,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T20:41:34.000Z","msg":"有一種想識朋友又唔想識朋友嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長期自閉好似會頹"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:17:21.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好羨慕其他人多朋友但自己又唔想晒時間晒心機去維繫 覺得社交好攰<br />\n獨家村咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其呢排日日係屋企 每日都好頹好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"839cccbfc0887db5d82cad386c6bb9170ff1683d","tid":2133071,"uid":326299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c60f6a5028226cf62e963b0a9708d9160b6456e","tid":2133071,"uid":144628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf892c22d45fea4da9b2f8a369543dfe4142b443","tid":2133071,"uid":326299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2364d0a0e75be5adbeb0796c80ff32800c5acba8","tid":2133071,"uid":144628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T20:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T20:43:58.000Z","msg":"咁我希望你可以快啲開心返，唔好成日都屈住自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\